metadata.name: The Outer Girls 01 Tako Gamer
metadata.description:
The Outer Girls
Kawaii Scary Things

Tako Gamer
She will come to play game with you
No matter what game you are playing
Even you're not connected to the Internet 
She can find you

Rule is
If you lose, you die
If you win, you die

If you treat her with Takoyaki, you live.
If Takoyaki is not tasty, you die
